caption: @JackandJackOfficial @JackGilinskyOfficial @JackJohnsonOfficial I've been waiting for almost 3 years to meet my idols and nothing I want more in life is to meet my idols who go me over being bullied and harassed by kids at my school and when the day comes for me to meet them I'll hug them so tight and never let go?? I wish they come back to Boston soon cause I can't wait any longer to meet them? I saw them at Digifest MA but the meet and greet for GA got cancelled and that was my one chance to meet them cause I couldn't meet them in Boston for the Verizon opening (I had a placement test fort freshman year)? I want to meet them so bad words can't explain it? I love these boys with all my heart??
